text: Scott M. Jensen (born November 19, 1954) is an American physician and politician. He is a member of the Republican Party. He was a member of the Minnesota Senate from 2017 to 2021. He was the Republican nominee for governor of Minnesota in the 2022 election, however lost the election to Governor Tim Walz. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
